import { Box, TextField } from '@mui/material'
import React from 'react'
import styles from './NewUserForm.style'
const newUserForm = () => {
    return (
       <> <TextField
  hiddenLabel
  id="filled-hidden-label-small"
  defaultValue="Small"
  variant="filled"
  size="small"
/>
<TextField
  hiddenLabel
  id="filled-hidden-label-normal"
  defaultValue="Normal"
  variant="filled"
/>
</>
    )
}

export default newUserForm
